name: The Seer
description:
The Seer is the insight to the soul. It is rich with wisdom, wielding knowledge of the beginning and the end. The Seer watches over all, and it is simply everything while being nothing at the same time. The Seer is watching.

Video format: .mp4



Created by @CuddleofDeath on October 11th, 2021 using her original art combined with AI synthesis technology (VQGAN+CLIP).
